caption.text: Watching a thing on Vox (via @jkottke ) about snails in  illuminated medieval manuscripts it struck me that the images are outlined.  Lots of contemporary comics folks say outlined drawings are artifacts of the printing process, but this demonstrates other concerns may be involved.  #sketchbook
